#Text=Guard # 1 says : " How many push - ups did you do last night ?
#Text=Get back to work !
#Text=" Aiwei says : " Is everything all right here ?
#Text=" Lin says : " The Avatar is in danger , and these two knuckleheads are just standing around chit - chatting .
#Text=" Aiwei says : " Do n't worry , Zaofu is the most secure city in the world .
#Text=" Lin says : " I 'll be the judge of that .
#Text=I 'm going to check every inch of this place .
#Text=" Aiwei says : " Lin , you do not have to work while you are here .
#Text=You need to relax .
#Text=" Lin says : " I 'm fine !
#Text=" Aiwei says : " It does n't take a truth seer to know that you are under a dangerous amount of stress .
#Text=If you do n't deal with your suppressed feelings , there will be severe consequences to your health ... and your job .
#Text=" Lin says : " I 'm not interested in talking about my feelings .
#Text=" Aiwei says : " You wo n't have to say a word .
#Text=I know a great acupuncturist in town who will be able to help you .
#Text=" Lin says : " Hmm .
#Text="
